title: Supreme Court Hands Republicans an Enormous Redistricting Win, Reinstates Map Struck Down by Lower Court
description: A map that would put Texas in a position to add five Republican congressional seats is back in play after a Supreme Court action.
content:
The Supreme Court on Thursday handed Republicans a major victory in the multi-state chess game of redrawing congressional district lines ahead of the 2026 midterm elections.
